BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (INTERPRETATIONS \(what you tell yourself about the event\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (- 'They did it on purpose') Tj ET
