BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 216.0 750 Td (OPPOSITE ACTION FOR ANGER) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (Opposite Action is the #1 DBT skill for anger. When anger urges) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (say DO something destructive, you do the OPPOSITE instead.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (WHEN TO USE OPPOSITE ACTION:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (- When acting on anger would make things WORSE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (- When anger is not justified by the facts) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (- When anger is justified but acting on it is ineffective) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (ANGER'S ACTION URGES vs OPPOSITE ACTIONS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (Urge: Attack/criticize  -->  Opposite: Gently avoid or be kind) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (Urge: Yell/raise voice  -->  Opposite: Speak softly and slowly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (Urge: Slam/throw things -->  Opposite: Relax hands, unclench) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td (Urge: Storm out         -->  Opposite: Stay \(or leave calmly\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (Urge: Give silent treat -->  Opposite: Communicate directly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (Urge: Seek revenge      -->  Opposite: Let go or problem-solve) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (Urge: Ruminate/obsess   -->  Opposite: Distract, do something else) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (HOW TO DO OPPOSITE ACTION FULLY:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (1. Identify the action urge \(what does anger want me to do?\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (2. Identify the opposite \(what would a calm person do?\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (3. Do the opposite ALL THE WAY \(body, face, words, posture\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (4. Repeat until the emotion changes intensity) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (IMPORTANT: Do this with WILLINGNESS, not white-knuckling.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (Opposite action done resentfully doesn't work as well.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td (MY PRACTICE:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td (My typical anger urge: ____________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 251 Td (My opposite action: _______________________________________) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
