BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 205.2 750 Td (TIPP SKILLS FOR RAGE MOMENTS) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (TIPP is for CRISIS moments when anger is at 8-10/10 and you) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (need to change your body chemistry FAST before you do damage.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (T = TEMPERATURE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (  Dunk your face in ice water for 30 seconds \(or hold ice on face\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (  This triggers the dive reflex and immediately slows heart rate) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (  HOW: Bowl of ice water, lean face in. Or ice pack on eyes/cheeks) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (  SCIENCE: Activates parasympathetic nervous system instantly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (I = INTENSE EXERCISE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (  Do vigorous exercise for 15-20 minutes to burn off adrenaline) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (  Sprint, jump rope, climb stairs, pushups - anything HARD) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (  HOW: Immediately start moving. Don't think, just move.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td (  SCIENCE: Metabolizes stress hormones, releases endorphins) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (P = PACED BREATHING) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td (  Breathe out LONGER than you breathe in) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (  Inhale 4 counts, exhale 6-8 counts. Repeat 10+ times) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (  HOW: Breathe from belly, not chest. Slow way down.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (  SCIENCE: Activates vagus nerve, reduces fight-or-flight) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (P = PAIRED MUSCLE RELAXATION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (  Tense muscles while breathing in, relax while breathing out) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td (  Start with fists, then arms, shoulders, face, whole body) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (  HOW: Hold tension 5 sec, release. Notice the contrast.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (  SCIENCE: Releases physical holding patterns of anger) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 299 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 283 Td (USE TIPP WHEN: You are about to explode. These are EMERGENCY tools.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td (Use them BEFORE trying to talk or make decisions.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
