BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 226.8 750 Td (DEAR MAN WHILE FURIOUS) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 214.8 732 Td (Interpersonal Effectiveness When Angry) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 722 m 562 722 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 700 Td (DEAR MAN is the DBT skill for asking for what you want effectively.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 684 Td (Here's how to use it when anger makes you want to DEMAND:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 668 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 652 Td (D = DESCRIBE \(just the facts, no interpretation\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 636 Td (  'When I got home, the dishes were still in the sink.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 620 Td (  NOT: 'You never do anything around here!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 604 Td (  Practice: _____________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 588 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 572 Td (E = EXPRESS \(how you feel, using I-statements\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 556 Td (  'I feel frustrated and overwhelmed.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 540 Td (  NOT: 'You make me so angry!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 524 Td (  Practice: _____________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 508 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 492 Td (A = ASSERT \(what you want, specifically\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 476 Td (  'I need us to split chores evenly.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 460 Td (  NOT: 'Figure it out!' or 'You should know!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 444 Td (  Practice: _____________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 428 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 412 Td (R = REINFORCE \(why they'd want to help\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 396 Td (  'If we share the load, we'll both be less stressed and fight less.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td (  Practice: _____________________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 364 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 348 Td (M = MINDFUL \(stay on topic, don't get derailed\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 332 Td (  If they deflect: 'I hear that, and I want to stay on this topic.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 316 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 300 Td (A = APPEAR CONFIDENT \(even when shaking inside\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 284 Td (  Eye contact, steady voice, upright posture) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 268 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 252 Td (N = NEGOTIATE \(be willing to give to get\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 236 Td (  'What would work for both of us?') Tj ET

endstream
