BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 234.0 750 Td (MINDFULNESS OF ANGER) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 248.4 732 Td (Observing Without Acting) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 722 m 562 722 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 700 Td (Mindfulness means OBSERVING your anger without becoming it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 684 Td (You are not your anger. Anger is something passing through you.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 668 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 652 Td (THE OBSERVE SKILL:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 636 Td (Notice anger as it arises. Watch it like weather:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 620 Td ('I notice a sensation of heat in my chest.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 604 Td ('I notice the thought that this is unfair.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 588 Td ('I notice the urge to raise my voice.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 572 Td (You are the observer, not the anger itself.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 556 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 540 Td (THE DESCRIBE SKILL:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 524 Td (Put words on your experience without judgment:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 508 Td ('Anger is here. It feels hot and tight.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 492 Td (NOT: 'I'm so angry I could explode!' \(this escalates\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 476 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 460 Td (THE PARTICIPATE SKILL:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 444 Td (Fully feel the anger without adding to it:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 428 Td (- Don't suppress it \(makes it worse\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 412 Td (- Don't amplify it \(rehearsing why you're right\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 396 Td (- Just let it BE without acting on it) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 364 Td (PRACTICE: Next time anger arises, try this:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 348 Td (1. Pause. Don't speak or act for 3 breaths.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 332 Td (2. Name it: 'Anger is here.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 316 Td (3. Notice where it is in your body: ________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 300 Td (4. Rate it 1-10: ___) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 284 Td (5. Watch it. Does it stay the same? Grow? Shrink?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 268 Td (6. Remind yourself: 'I can feel this AND choose my action.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 252 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 236 Td (IMPORTANT: Emotions are like waves. If you don't feed them,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 220 Td (they WILL peak and then decrease. Every single time.) Tj ET

endstream
