BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (O - Observe what's happening inside and outside you) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td (P - Proceed mindfully \(choose, don't react\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (DISTRACTION \(ACCEPTS\):) Tj ET
